Are you here by yourself'?

10
00:05:06.256 --> 00:05:07.823
Mostly.

11
00:05:07.824 --> 00:05:09.258
More coffee?

12
00:05:09.259 --> 00:05:11.068
Please.

13
00:05:14.831 --> 00:05:16.674
No milk.

14
